        "title": "fix: clean egress daemons during lease stop",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add best-effort mediated egress cleanup before ordinary SSH lease release\n- stop local host daemon state for both the requested identifier and resolved lease ID when they differ\n- SSH-kill the lease-side egress client when a target is available, warning without blocking release\n- document that `crabbox stop` includes mediated egress cleanup\n\nCloses https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/481\n\n## Validation\n- go test ./internal/cli -run 'TestStopCleansMediatedEgressBeforeRelease|TestReleaseBackendLeaseBestEffortCleansMediatedEgressBeforeRelease|TestEgressStopUsesSharedRemoteClientStopCommand'\n- go test -race ./internal/cli\n- go vet ./...\n- bash scripts/check-docs.sh\n\n## Release notes\n- `crabbox stop` now best-effort cleans up daemonized mediated egress state before releasing SSH leases.\n",
